        <div class="section" id="products">
          <div class="full-content">

            <h1>Our Products</h1>
            <a id="fogbugz" class="product" href="/web/20110423221819/http://www.fogcreek.com:80/fogbugz/" title="Learn more about FogBugz">
                <span class="product-header">FogBugz: Bug and Issue Tracking and Project Management</span>
                <span class="product-body">
                  FogBugz manages projects, tracks bugs, and 
                  even tells you when you’re going to ship.
                  It includes an issue tracker, advanced project management and scheduling,
                  a wiki, and customer support features like email routing and discussion groups.
                </span>
                <span class="product-more">More about FogBugz &raquo;</span>
            </a>

            <a id="kiln" class="product" href="/web/20110423221819/http://www.fogcreek.com:80/kiln/" title="Learn more about Kiln">    
                <span class="product-header">Kiln: Mercurial DVCS (Distributed Version Control System) with code reviews and repository management</span>
                <span class="product-body">
                  Kiln is a complete version control system
                  based on Mercurial. That means it's got branching
                  and merging that really work!  Plus
                  a really awesome code review system, repository management, code search 
                  and FogBugz integration.  And set up is a snap.
                </span>
                <span class="product-more">More about Kiln &raquo;</span>
            </a>   

            <a id="copilot" class="product" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20110423221819/http://www.copilot.com/" title="Learn more about Copilot">
                <span class="product-header">Fog Creek Copilot</span>
                <span class="product-body">
                  Fog Creek Copilot helps you 
                  provide tech support remotely, over the Internet. 
                  Connect to anyone’s computer&mdash;Windows or Macintosh. 
                  See what they see, control their mouse and keyboard, and fix the
                  issue.  No installation or configuration.
                </span>  
                <span class="product-more">More about Copilot &raquo;</span>
            </a>

          </div>
        </div>


